<p><b>  Urgent appeals 
</b></p>
<p>206. The Working Group transmitted on 17 October 2012, jointly with one other special 
procedures mechanism, a communication under its urgent appeal procedure, concerning 
Mr. <b>Ashraf Mohammed Yousef Abdulsalam, </b>arrested on 25 September 2012 at his home 
in Bahrain by agents of the Bahraini State Security Forces. He was reportedly later forcibly 
returned to Jordan without further information being provided on his fate and whereabouts 
in spite of requests thereof. At the time of the communication, his fate and whereabouts 
reportedly remained unknown. 
