<p><b>  Request for a visit 
</b></p>
<p>287. On 12 May 2006, the Working Group requested to undertake a follow-up visit to 
Nepal. A reminder letter was transmitted on 20 July 2009. On 2 October 2009, the 
Government informed the Working Group that due to the limited capacities of the country 
and other engagements it was unable to extend an invitation. A new reminder letter was 
transmitted on 30 June 2011. No reply has been received. 
</p>
<p><b>  Total cases transmitted, clarified and outstanding 
</b></p>
