<p>438. The Working Group sent one case under its urgent action procedure to the 
Government. It concerned Mr. <b>Naimjon Atokhonovich Naimkhonov</b>, who was allegedly 
last seen near the bus station of Karabolo district, Dushanbe, on 8 August 2012.  
</p>
